summary: Help me build the base set!
title: Help me build the base set!
body:
PART ONE: www.surveymonkey.com/r/DWL9M2R
PART TWO: www.surveymonkey.com/r/DMDZZ9F

I’m building the set list for the first base set, and instead of just picking my own favorites, I’d like to get some feedback from whomever wants to respond! This is as easy to selecting your favorite Pokemon, and should give me a good starting point for building something we can all be excited about!

Thanks for your help! :-D

(PS I couldn’t finagle SurveyMonkey into limiting responses to 4 per question. Please abide by this cap as you respond - not that it matters terribly much either way.)
